	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Superhot Fire</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_HELP">
			<Text>Word from our man at the Volcano, Your Magnanimousness. I think it's good news this time, though I can't always tell with him.[NEWLINE]Shall I read it out?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Sacrificing the Fire King and -1 [ICON_POPULATION] Population causes Krakatoa to yield +3 [ICON_PEACE] Faith, and begins {4_Turns} of WLTKD.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Nearby Jungles yield an additional +2 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Nearby Atolls yield +5 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*As you know, superheated magma from the Earth's core is expelled from the crust in a proces...*[NEWLINE]Basically he's found out something new? Wonderful, add it to the Library.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The local religious leaders follow very strange astronomical rituals, that are most remininscent of those islanders I met over in...*[NEWLINE]He's found a solution to that religious dispute? Very good, give him the go ahead.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The local fauna are incredible, Your Grace. It must be emphasised that I haven't seen a climax ecosystem like this in all my travels, even on that one expedition up Mount...*[NEWLINE]More Sciency things? Good good, forward this to my Science Advisor, I'll let him deal with it.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_VOLCANO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*I must preface this letter with a note of extreme caution, for there are few men with an imagination strong enough to comprehend the possiblity I am about to divulge to you in this correspondance! I believe that the Atolls of the Molten Coast are, in fact, relatively new! I know! How incredible the tectonic proce...*[NEWLINE]I'm sorry, I dozed off. You know the drill, forward everything to my Science Advisor.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
